@startuml fcr_state_machine
' =============================================================================
' FCR ROS2 Workspace — State Machine Diagram (Servo Lifecycle)
' =============================================================================

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam stateBorderColor #333333
skinparam stateBackgroundColor #EEF5FF

title VisualServo Action — 状态机 (State Machine)

[*] --> IDLE

state "IDLE\n(空闲)" as IDLE #LightGray {
  state "等待目标\nwaiting_for_target" as wait_target
  state "等待指令\nwaiting_for_command" as wait_cmd
}

state "CONVERGING\n(收敛中)" as CONVERGING #LightBlue {
  state "计算雅可比\ncompute_jacobian" as comp_jac
  state "计算控制律\ncompute_control" as comp_ctrl
  state "发布指令\npublish_cmds" as pub_cmd

  comp_jac --> comp_ctrl : L_s, cond(L)
  comp_ctrl --> pub_cmd : v_cam = -λ·pinv(L)·e
  pub_cmd --> comp_jac : 下一帧
}

state "TRACKING\n(跟踪中/已收敛)" as TRACKING #LightGreen
state "LOST\n(目标丢失)" as LOST #Orange
state "ERROR\n(错误)" as ERROR #Red

' ── Transitions ──

IDLE --> CONVERGING : VisualServo Action Goal\n+ 目标出现

CONVERGING --> TRACKING : ||e|| < tolerance\n(已收敛)

CONVERGING --> LOST : 目标超出视野\n或跟踪ID失效
CONVERGING --> ERROR : cond(L) > threshold\n(雅可比奇异)

TRACKING --> CONVERGING : 目标移动\n||e|| > tolerance

TRACKING --> LOST : 目标丢失

LOST --> CONVERGING : 目标重新出现\n(Re-ID匹配成功)

LOST --> IDLE : 超时(timeout)\n或 Action Cancel

ERROR --> IDLE : 重置/恢复

IDLE --> [*] : Action Result\n(success/failure)

note right of CONVERGING
  <b>IBVS 控制循环 (50Hz)</b>
  1. extractFeatures(target)
  2. e = s - s*
  3. L = interactionMatrix(s, Z)
  4. v = -λ · L⁺ · e
  5. allocate(v) → chassis + gimbal
end note

note right of ERROR
  <b>雅可比奇异常见原因:</b>
  · 目标在图像边缘
  · 深度估计为0
  · 3个特征点共线
  · 目标距离太远(Z→∞)

  <b>恢复策略:</b>
  · 降级为速度保持
  · 通知操作员
  · 可切换到PBVS模式
end note

note right of LOST
  <b>丢失恢复策略:</b>
  · ByteTrack保留ID N帧
  · 扩大搜索区域
  · 降低置信度阈值
  · 回退到检测模式
end note

@enduml
